You have inspired many people and I can proudly say I’m one of them. Your heart is so full and caring. You continue to make both myself and others happy. summary: Happy Birthday to the woman who changed mine, and so many other people's lives for the better! I know that @taylorswift will...
body:
Happy Birthday to the woman who changed mine, and so many other people’s lives for the better! I know that @taylorswift will probably never see this (and that this is probably the closest i’ll ever get to meeting her 😂), but on the off-chance that she does:

I love you so much.

Thank you for the inspiration you’ve been for the past 8 years of my life, I literally can’t thank you enough.

I am so glad you’re doing so much better than you ever were! I hope you spend your birthday with your loved ones, or doing what you love.

Make your 29th year as good (or better) as your 28th and the ones that came before that! 💜

And thank you so much.

I really hope to see you soon on tour for TS7 (please don’t skip Amsterdam this time 😉💜)

summary:
@taylorswift I'm not good with words, I have written and rewritten this about a million times lol. 
It's your 29th birthday! The...
body:
@taylorswift I’m not good with words, I have written and rewritten this about a million times lol.

It’s your 29th birthday! The end of a decade xD Look how much you have achieved in this 29 years, it is staggering and I can’t even begin to verbalize how proud I am of you, watching you from the very beginning and seeing where you are now. You’ve been the big sister that I never had, the friend I was never allowed to have, and the shoulder to cry on when I wasn’t allowed to cry. I’ve grown up with you and your words and it has been an amazing journey. Your strength is incredible and gives me hope. Your joy is infectious and brightens lives all over the world. You said once that if you could have a superpower it would be to heal people, you do have that superpower. You have healed millions, and continue to help them heal little by little every day. Thank you. So here’s to you, Taylor! 29 years old and so many accomplishments, and so much good you have injected into this harsh world. I hope your birthday is as wonderful as you are, and I hope that this year is kind and treats you well!!

Happy Birthday, Taylor!!!!

Love, Grace (I’ll have some champagne to celebrate the day here in Florida)

happy 29th birthday to my beautiful best friend!! I am so so proud of everything you have achieved in the last 29 years. You have truly changed my life and I won’t ever be able to thank you enough. I hope your day is filled with sunshine and glitter and cats and friends and family and Christmas!! I love you so much and can’t wait to see what amazing things you do at 29!! @taylorswift

Love, Ronnie
